    StructureDefinition-organization-deqm

    The DEQM Organization Profile defines the constraints for representing the organization for which the practitioner was working when he performed the measure to which he is attesting.

    Mandatory Data Elements and Terminology

    The following data-elements are mandatory (i.e data MUST be present).

    Each Organization must have:

    1. Either an NPI or EIN (TIN) identifier

    Additional Profile specific implementation guidance:

    None

    Examples

  • DaVinciHospital02
  • DaVinciHospital03
  • DVPayer04
  • DaVinciHospital01

    • Formal Views of Profile Content

    This profile builds on QICoreOrganization
